Package frc.inputs

Class OperatorGamepad

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.inputs.OperatorGamepad
  • public final class OperatorGamepad
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides an implementation of an GameHid to encapsulate all of the functions that the all of the active HID's, together, must provide. For most seasons, this essentially ties together the driver and operator gamepad functions into one simpler interface.

        public static OperatorGamepad getInstance()
        Returns a static instance of the OperatorGamepad class. If none has been created yet, the instance is created. This enables multiple any other classes to use this class without having to pass an instance or take the risk of trying to instantiate multiple instances of this class, which would result in errors.
